(80, 15, NULL, 'MG-R-20251222-63673', 'Jayesh Salve', '7744996608', 'salvejayesh777@gmail.com', 'Lithium Battery 48KW', '00', '1126', NULL, '2024-05-15', 'uploads/invoices/80/invoice.pdf', NULL, 'phone', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'The battery management system (BMS) of the battery is currently not communicating with the inverter, which is affecting the overall performance and monitoring of the system. Due to this communication failure, essential operational data such as battery voltage, current status, state of charge, and protection alerts are not being properly transmitted to the inverter. As a result, the inverter is unable to accurately recognize the battery condition or operate in an optimized and safe manner.\r\n\r\nIn addition to the communication issue, the battery display unit is not functioning. The display normally provides real-time information regarding battery parameters and system health; however, at present, it remains inactive or unresponsive. This makes it difficult to monitor the battery status and diagnose faults directly from the battery interface.\r\n\r\nFurthermore, the ON/OFF switch of the battery is also not working correctly. The battery does not respond consistently when the switch is operated, which creates difficulty in safely powering the system on or shutting it down when required. This malfunction increases the risk during maintenance and troubleshooting procedures.\r\n\r\nAt times, the system also shows error messages, indicating intermittent faults or internal protection triggers. These errors may be related to communication failure, internal BMS malfunction, wiring issues, or software-related problems. Overall, the combined issues of BMS–inverter communication failure, non-functional display, faulty ON/OFF switch, and recurring error indications suggest a serious operational fault that requires immediate technical inspection, proper diagnosis, and corrective action by qualified service personnel to restore normal and safe system operation.', NULL, 'Plot 10, Near Trilokeshwar Mahadev Temple, Shiv Colony, Amalner, Tal. Amalner, Dist. Jalgaon, Maharashtra', 'Amalner', '425401', '2025-12-22', 'Resolved on Call', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-01-10 08:12:33', '2025-12-22 05:17:19', '2026-01-10 08:12:33', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
