(252, NULL, NULL, 'MG-R-20260209-53570', 'Bimlesh Tripathi', '8051452124', 'tripathibimlesh123@gmail.com', 'MG2510090AM', 'MG2510090AM003', '71126000281347', NULL, '2025-10-09', 'uploads/invoices/252/invoice.pdf', NULL, 'hardware', 2, '2026-02-11 06:11:33', 2, 'The stabilizer is not turning on. It is turning on only after turning on the bypass. Later I have to turn off the bypass. It is running for 4 minutes and 3 minutes and is turning off automatically. The switch is also not falling, which means the connection is leaving the output and is reducing at 200 or 180 input voltage. When the input voltage is reduced below 180, the stabilizer is not reducing at all, whereas I had purchased it with the idea that even then the 90 in footer will give good output, but it is not working at all, it is just shut down.', NULL, 'Shivdatta colony Adarsh Nagar urli devachi pune', 'Pune', '412308', '2026-02-09', 'Hardware Service – Awaiting Label', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-02-09 03:16:02', '2026-02-10 06:11:33', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
