(255, NULL, NULL, 'MG-R-20260209-25910', 'DAVID J', '9486965846', 'davidongcpmk41@gmail.com', 'MG15130ML', 'MSN457MWG7RN9J', 'MO99408012602329', NULL, '2026-01-16', 'uploads/invoices/255/invoice.jpg', NULL, 'hardware', 2, '2026-02-22 07:01:38', 2, '15 kva Stabilizer out put volt very higher. Unit fault contion. Take action immediately return unit  further action.', NULL, 'David J. 6/454 g Rajiv nagar pambuvilunthan paramakudi Ramanathapuram dt. 623707', 'Paramakudi', '623707', '2026-02-12', 'Hardware Service – Awaiting Label', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-02-09 18:31:13', '2026-02-21 07:01:38', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(256, NULL, NULL, 'MG-R-20260210-65640', 'V V SURYA PRASAD CHITYALA', '8008123284', 'chityalaprasad28@gmail.com', '51.2V LFP', 'MGLIBAT120512', 'IN-220', NULL, '2025-11-25', 'uploads/invoices/256/invoice.pdf', NULL, 'hardware', 2, '2026-02-11 07:13:54', 2, 'I purchased the MuscleGrid 120AH Lithium Battery (51.2V, Smart LCD Model) under Order ID 408‑8874864‑0497928, delivered on 04 December 2025.\r\n\r\nThe battery has developed a serious issue after about two months of normal use. On 08 February 2026, the battery suddenly caused the MCB to trip unexpectedly when the battery was in use. After attempting to reset the MCB and pressing the start button on the battery, it switched on, but I soon heard a noise inside the battery that resembled a short circuit. For safety I immediately disconnected the battery and switched the system to mains.\r\n\r\nI verified:\r\n\r\nMy inverter (Surja 5500 PRO) is functioning normally\r\nLoad conditions were within safe limits\r\nNo wiring or connection issues\r\nSince the problem appears to be internal to the battery, I request your assistance in resolving this at the earliest. Please advise on the next steps for inspection, or warranty support.\r\n\r\nThank you for your prompt attention. I look forward to your response.', NULL, 'Ch v v s Prasad\r\nD No: 9-4-2/1, \r\nBehind Veterinary Hospital, \r\nNehru Nagar,', 'nidadavole', '534301', '0000-00-00', 'Hardware Service – Awaiting Label', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-02-10 05:58:55', '2026-02-10 07:13:54', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
