(287, NULL, NULL, 'MG-R-20260220-92154', 'Tapan Ditta', '8340223971', '', 'MG solarstar 6kW inverter', 'Will send later', 'MGIG25-26/0216', NULL, '2025-08-26', 'uploads/invoices/287/invoice.pdf', NULL, 'phone', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'I have solarstar 6kW inverter with 48v musclegrid LFP battery (no solar input connected). The inverter\'s fan is constantly on high speed, making lot of noise while mains is available. But during powercut and on battery power, the fans are silent.\r\n\r\nAlso, on the inverter display, it shows battery is charging. But battery shows 99-100% with 0A current flow. So inverter is trying to charge battery, but battery is not accepting charge. How to make sure inverter knows state-of-charge of battery and does not make too much noise? I have already connected RS232 ports with ethernet cable.\r\n\r\nAlso, please send the inverter and battery manual in pdf format. the manual on your website is not for the solarstar inverter. And we also need the wifi adapter for inverter monitoring on app.', NULL, 'House-11, Pragjyotishnagar (main road), BG colony, Maligaon, Guwahati, Assam 781011', 'Guwahati', '781011', '2026-02-24', 'Resolved on Call', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-02-21 06:27:21', '2026-02-20 10:42:03', '2026-02-21 06:27:21', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
